OL,3,CDisabled teen left alone during school
OL,4,Cfire takes campaign to parliament
OL,6,FLucas spoke to Susanna Reid and Ed
OL,7,FBalls about his campaign on Good
OL,8,FMorning Britain.
OL,10,FA teenage boy who was left alone
OL,11,Fupstairs during a school fire has
OL,12,Ftaken his campaign for stronger safety
OL,13,Frules for disabled students to
OL,14,FParliament.
OL,16,FLucas Vezza-O'Brien has cerebral palsy
OL,17,Fand says he was "terrified" when smoke
OL,18,Fbegan to fill the corridor on the
OL,19,Ffirst floor of his school in Hyde,
OL,20,FGreater Manchester, in November 2024.
