OL,3,CDisabled teen left alone during school
OL,4,Cfire takes campaign to parliament
OL,6,FLucas was told to stay at a refuge
OL,7,Fpoint while the rest of his fellow
OL,8,Fpupils were taken out of the building.
OL,10,FHe said: "It was petrifying...I kept
OL,11,Fgetting checked on, but I could smell
OL,12,Fsmoke. We all know the biggest killer
OL,13,Fin a fire is smoke and it could have
OL,14,Fbeen easily avoided."
OL,16,FLucas uses a wheelchair, and was
OL,17,Funable to leave the school because
OL,18,Fthere was no safe way to get him down
OL,19,Fthe stairs and out of the building.
