OL,6,FA Hyde High School spokesperson said
OL,7,FLucas was looked after in a designated
OL,8,Frefuge area which is protected from
OL,9,Ffire and smoke and was checked on
OL,10,Fregularly while a plan was made to get
OL,11,Fhim out of the building safely.
OL,13,FBut Lucas said the whole experience
OL,14,Fwas terrifying and made him feel
OL,15,Fpowerless.
OL,17,FHe said: "It's inhumane. If you let me
OL,18,Fin the building, let me get out."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
