OL,3,CDisabled teen left alone during school
OL,4,Cfire takes campaign to parliament
OL,6,FThe fire turned out to be minor, but
OL,7,Fthe scare has sparked a powerful
OL,8,Fcampaign. The teenager is now calling
OL,9,Ffor evacuation chairs to be made a
OL,10,Flegal requirement in every school.
OL,12,FEvacuation chairs are specially
OL,13,Fdesigned to be used by people with
OL,14,Flimited mobility to get down stairs
OL,15,Fduring emergencies such as a fire when
OL,16,Flifts are unsafe to use.
OL,18,FThere is currently no legal
OL,19,Frequirement for schools to have
OL,20,Fevacuation chairs installed; something
OL,21,FLucas is hoping to change.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
