OL,3,CDisabled teen left alone during school
OL,4,Cfire takes campaign to parliament
OL,6,FLucas said: "After it happened, I
OL,7,Fresearched the current legislation and
OL,8,FI was shocked to see that schools
OL,9,Fdon't have evac-chairs.
OL,11,F"They might be costly but you can't
OL,12,Fput a price on my life, or other
OL,13,Fpeople's."
OL,15,FSince launching the petition, more
OL,16,Fthan 100,000 have backed his campaign
OL,17,Fand now MPs will debate the
OL,18,Fintroduction of mandatory evacuation
OL,19,Fchairs in the House of Commons.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
