OL,6,FLucas said: "I opened the petition,
OL,7,Fand now I've got 104,000 signatures.
OL,8,FIt's a pinch me moment. If you told me
OL,9,Flast year I'd get 10,000 I'd say
OL,10,Fyou're silly, so I'm amazed."
OL,12,FLucas' campaigning has already made a
OL,13,Fdifference at his own high school,
OL,14,Fwhere four evacuation chairs have been
OL,15,Ffitted to ensure he never has to be
OL,16,Fleft behind again.
